1
00:00:11,380 --> 00:00:15,783
<i>Hey boys, listen up!</i>

2
00:00:15,851 --> 00:00:20,379
<i>Humans aren't such a big deal</i>

3
00:00:21,089 --> 00:00:25,219
<i>Who needs tomorrow anyway,</i>

4
00:00:25,294 --> 00:00:28,491
<i>so don't hide your fists</i>

5
00:00:30,432 --> 00:00:32,696
<i>You're not old enough</i>

6
00:00:32,768 --> 00:00:39,071
<i>to sell your dreams away to uncertainty</i>

7
00:00:40,008 --> 00:00:44,445
<i>Hey boys, you're the only ones</i>

8
00:00:44,513 --> 00:00:48,040
<i>who can pull the trigger in your heart</i>

9
00:00:49,484 --> 00:00:51,418
<i>All the kids said</i>

10
00:00:51,486 --> 00:00:54,421
<i>We're living in this senseless, ridiculous,</i>

11
00:00:54,489 --> 00:00:58,789
<i>awesome world right at this moment,</i>

12
00:00:58,994 --> 00:01:01,258
<i>All the kids said</i>

13
00:01:01,330 --> 00:01:07,132
<i>Don't forget every truth or lie</i>

14
00:01:08,537 --> 00:01:10,872
<i>All the kids said</i>

15
00:01:10,872 --> 00:01:13,204
<i>We're way too young to die</i>

16
00:01:13,275 --> 00:01:18,076
<i>In this empty town lined with empty faces</i>

17
00:01:18,146 --> 00:01:20,341
<i>All the kids took off</i>

18
00:01:20,415 --> 00:01:22,883
<i>into this windless night</i>

19
00:01:22,951 --> 00:01:26,318
<i>Because they want to change something</i>

20
00:01:31,403 --> 00:01:35,601
<i>The Promise That Could Not Be Kept</i>

21
00:01:44,683 --> 00:01:46,014
Kakashi Sensei...

22
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:49,748
Where's Sasuke?

23
00:01:57,196 --> 00:01:58,220
Kakashi!

24
00:01:59,364 --> 00:02:00,888
How is Naruto Uzumaki's condition?

25
00:02:01,433 --> 00:02:02,627
He's okay.

26
00:02:03,168 --> 00:02:06,831
What about Sasuke?
Where's Sasuke Uchiha?!

27
00:02:21,587 --> 00:02:23,350
How are the other Genin?

28
00:02:23,722 --> 00:02:26,156
Yes! By Lady Hokage's order,

29
00:02:26,225 --> 00:02:28,386
the first and second medical corps
have been dispatched...

30
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:30,960
The wounded from all areas have
already been gathered.

31
00:02:31,330 --> 00:02:34,822
They were convoyed after
administering emergency treatment.

32
00:02:35,234 --> 00:02:36,360
How are their conditions?

33
00:02:36,435 --> 00:02:39,233
Yes! Shikamaru Nara has minor injuries...

34
00:02:39,538 --> 00:02:44,066
Kiba Inuzuka has serious injuries,
but it's not life threatening.

35
00:02:44,543 --> 00:02:48,411
Neji Hyuga and Choji Akimichi
are in serious condition...

36
00:02:49,214 --> 00:02:51,273
At this point,
there's no telling what will happen.

37
00:03:05,831 --> 00:03:07,025
<i>Everyone...</i>

38
00:03:27,185 --> 00:03:29,483
<i>The ingredients and</i>
<i>effects of the medicine</i>

39
00:03:29,554 --> 00:03:31,522
<i>have been thoroughly researched.</i>

40
00:03:32,591 --> 00:03:34,252
<i>Excellent...</i>

41
00:03:35,060 --> 00:03:36,584
Now bring the deer antler!

42
00:03:36,862 --> 00:03:37,521
Yes, ma'am!

43
00:03:42,734 --> 00:03:44,702
How is he... Big Sister?

44
00:03:52,177 --> 00:03:54,236
No walks for him for quite a while...

45
00:03:54,313 --> 00:03:56,304
The muscles of his limbs
have been severely damaged.

46
00:03:56,682 --> 00:03:59,310
You're a vet, right, Big Sister?
Can't you somehow...?

47
00:03:59,384 --> 00:04:00,510
It'll be okay.

48
00:04:00,786 --> 00:04:05,120
It'll take time. But there's no threat
to his life, so rest easy.

49
00:04:08,493 --> 00:04:11,087
Walks for you are out of the question
for quite a while, too!

50
00:04:12,998 --> 00:04:14,898
Yeah, I know...

51
00:04:17,636 --> 00:04:20,730
Intensive Care Unit 7

52
00:04:29,214 --> 00:04:32,411
It'll soon be three hours...
Please take over.

53
00:04:32,751 --> 00:04:33,683
All right!

54
00:04:33,752 --> 00:04:36,846
Although we're making
this kid's hair into a conductor,

55
00:04:36,922 --> 00:04:40,119
please don't mistake the cellular rate
of the deficient parts!

56
00:04:40,425 --> 00:04:41,653
Right!

57
00:04:42,361 --> 00:04:44,886
As for the Chakra control, handle it
as if we're threading a needle!

58
00:04:45,230 --> 00:04:46,197
Understood!

59
00:04:56,341 --> 00:04:59,469
Intensive Care Unit 6

60
00:05:09,421 --> 00:05:11,946
There's no point in
you getting frustrated, right?

61
00:05:13,425 --> 00:05:15,655
Missions come with sacrifice...

62
00:05:15,994 --> 00:05:18,224
You took the mental training, right?

63
00:05:22,334 --> 00:05:25,064
Training and actual battle
are different, you know...

64
00:05:25,470 --> 00:05:28,234
I know what missions are about...

65
00:05:28,940 --> 00:05:32,398
And I thought I knew what
the Shinobi world is like.

66
00:05:34,379 --> 00:05:39,112
I became a platoon leader
for the first time on this mission.

67
00:05:39,518 --> 00:05:41,179
With that, I understood...

68
00:05:42,220 --> 00:05:44,381
I'm not cut out to be a Shinobi.

69
00:05:47,392 --> 00:05:50,987
Surprisingly fragile... for a man.

70
00:05:52,597 --> 00:05:53,962
This time...

71
00:05:54,032 --> 00:05:57,092
The only thing I was able to do
as platoon leader...

72
00:05:57,602 --> 00:05:59,832
was to believe in everyone.

73
00:06:00,972 --> 00:06:02,462
I was naïve...

74
00:06:02,841 --> 00:06:04,866
I didn't have enough power...

75
00:06:05,510 --> 00:06:07,102
It's all my fault!

76
00:06:08,346 --> 00:06:10,371
Are you afraid of getting hurt?

77
00:06:23,462 --> 00:06:24,986
Shikamaru...

78
00:06:26,731 --> 00:06:29,894
Are you going to be argued down
by a girl and run away?

79
00:06:31,069 --> 00:06:32,468
It's a drag...

80
00:06:32,537 --> 00:06:36,337
I don't want to have arguments.
I'm not a woman.

81
00:06:36,675 --> 00:06:40,042
Yeah... But you're not a man, either.

82
00:06:40,512 --> 00:06:42,912
You're just a coward!

83
00:06:43,582 --> 00:06:46,278
Even if you quit being Shinobi,
the missions will continue.

84
00:06:46,852 --> 00:06:49,218
Someone has to do it.

85
00:06:49,955 --> 00:06:53,288
Your comrades will just
be dispatched again...

86
00:06:53,358 --> 00:06:55,553
under a different platoon leader.

87
00:06:55,827 --> 00:06:58,887
And your comrades might die there.

88
00:06:59,297 --> 00:07:02,664
But if at that time,
<i>you</i> were the platoon leader...

89
00:07:02,734 --> 00:07:05,965
your comrades might be saved
from that happening to them.

90
00:07:06,838 --> 00:07:10,501
If you reflect on this time,
make use of the experience and learn,

91
00:07:10,575 --> 00:07:14,033
you might be able to carry out missions
with more perfection.

92
00:07:16,381 --> 00:07:19,441
If you really think your comrades
are important to you,

93
00:07:19,518 --> 00:07:22,009
before you think about running away...

94
00:07:22,087 --> 00:07:27,150
think about becoming more exceptional
for the sake of your comrades!

95
00:07:27,592 --> 00:07:32,256
That's what real comrades are,
you coward!

96
00:07:38,603 --> 00:07:40,833
Intensive Care Unit 6

97
00:07:53,552 --> 00:07:55,281
He's okay, now!

98
00:07:57,822 --> 00:08:00,052
The antidote has stopped
the death of cells

99
00:08:00,125 --> 00:08:03,583
caused by the side effects of the Pills.

100
00:08:04,129 --> 00:08:06,654
You were a big help this time, Shikaku!

101
00:08:07,332 --> 00:08:10,995
The Nara Clan's secret medicinal
preparation manual was very useful.

102
00:08:12,804 --> 00:08:15,705
It must've been tough to
make something like that...

103
00:08:16,274 --> 00:08:18,708
It's the result of day to day study.

104
00:08:19,077 --> 00:08:20,169
Thanks...

105
00:08:20,645 --> 00:08:21,703
Lady Tsunade!

106
00:08:26,952 --> 00:08:30,319
Neji Hyugan.
His safety line has been secured.

107
00:08:33,425 --> 00:08:35,655
And, there's some information...

108
00:08:36,061 --> 00:08:40,521
Kakashi Hatake and Naruto Uzumaki
have just now returned.

109
00:08:41,166 --> 00:08:45,193
Although seriously injured,
it seems it's not life threatening.

110
00:08:55,614 --> 00:08:56,911
Two, huh?

111
00:08:57,449 --> 00:09:01,283
Shikamaru...
It seems the mission is a failure.

112
00:09:05,924 --> 00:09:10,258
But, everyone is alive!
That's the most important thing.

113
00:09:15,500 --> 00:09:17,263
Next time for sure...

114
00:09:17,335 --> 00:09:19,394
I'll carry out the mission perfectly!

115
00:09:35,620 --> 00:09:39,056
Sasuke... You're the chosen one.

116
00:09:39,624 --> 00:09:43,390
Whatever... Just give me "power."

117
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:53,162
Even though the form is different,
it's still Lord Orochimaru before your eyes.

118
00:09:53,672 --> 00:09:56,903
If you don't want to die,
use more care in how you talk.

119
00:10:00,345 --> 00:10:02,711
<i>Wh-What? This quality of Chakra...</i>

120
00:10:03,115 --> 00:10:07,711
<i>Yes... My future is inside this kid...</i>

121
00:10:08,053 --> 00:10:10,749
Hidden Leaf Hospital

122
00:10:20,532 --> 00:10:22,932
<i>I'm going to where Orochimaru is!</i>

123
00:10:23,969 --> 00:10:28,030
<i>Please...bring back Sasuke!</i>

124
00:10:30,175 --> 00:10:35,374
<i>I'll bring Sasuke back without fail!</i>
<i>I promise that on my life!</i>

125
00:10:43,555 --> 00:10:46,285
Oh... You were awake, huh?

126
00:10:47,526 --> 00:10:48,857
Shikamaru!

127
00:10:53,131 --> 00:10:56,623
I'm going on ahead to Choji!
What about you?

128
00:10:57,135 --> 00:11:00,730
I'm going on ahead to...
Naruto and Sasuke!

129
00:11:01,537 --> 00:11:06,269
I see... So everyone's okay.
That's good.

130
00:11:11,516 --> 00:11:13,677
Then, Sasuke...

131
00:11:15,620 --> 00:11:18,088
Yeah... he's gone.

132
00:11:33,905 --> 00:11:36,499
Intensive Care Unit 6

133
00:11:36,908 --> 00:11:39,001
Then, I still can't see him...?

134
00:11:39,945 --> 00:11:44,814
Yeah... But Lady Tsunade said that
he should regain consciousness soon.

135
00:11:46,818 --> 00:11:48,285
Thank goodness...

136
00:11:49,054 --> 00:11:50,783
It's really a great help that

137
00:11:50,856 --> 00:11:53,450
Lady Tsunade returned
to the Leaf Village.

138
00:11:54,526 --> 00:11:56,926
If she hadn't, right about now,
Choji would be...

139
00:11:59,130 --> 00:12:02,566
<i>The Lady Fifth...Hokage.</i>

140
00:12:12,511 --> 00:12:13,739
You've come to visit?

141
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,975
Information sure travels fast.

142
00:12:23,722 --> 00:12:25,053
<i>Sakura...</i>

143
00:12:26,324 --> 00:12:27,382
Naruto...

144
00:12:32,797 --> 00:12:35,357
I heard you suffered
quite a serious injury...

145
00:12:35,934 --> 00:12:37,868
But you look well, considering.

146
00:12:42,741 --> 00:12:45,107
I'm sorry... Sakura...

147
00:12:48,747 --> 00:12:50,681
Why do you apologize?

148
00:12:56,354 --> 00:12:59,585
Being you, you probably
got reckless again, right?!

149
00:12:59,991 --> 00:13:02,619
Jeez, you look like a mummy...

150
00:13:03,962 --> 00:13:06,396
I'm sorry... I...

151
00:13:07,065 --> 00:13:11,729
Hey... The weather's nice today.
So open the curtains.

152
00:13:16,474 --> 00:13:18,465
Sakura! I...

153
00:13:18,543 --> 00:13:21,011
I'll keep my promise, no matter what!

154
00:13:21,413 --> 00:13:25,440
I promised on my life.
That's what I said, so I...!

155
00:13:27,519 --> 00:13:30,682
It's okay already, Naruto...

156
00:13:31,957 --> 00:13:33,447
Sakura! He...

157
00:13:33,525 --> 00:13:35,083
I always...

158
00:13:35,760 --> 00:13:38,285
said that, so... I...

159
00:13:38,930 --> 00:13:41,956
I never go back on my word!

160
00:13:42,434 --> 00:13:44,834
That's my Way of Ninja!

161
00:14:03,989 --> 00:14:05,047
Naruto...

162
00:14:09,127 --> 00:14:11,357
<i>Thanks, Naruto...</i>

163
00:14:16,601 --> 00:14:20,833
<i>I'll get right to healing this injury</i>
<i>and I've got to bring Sasuke back!</i>

164
00:14:24,009 --> 00:14:25,943
Wh-What was that?!

165
00:14:30,582 --> 00:14:32,675
Per... Pervy Saget?!

166
00:14:33,685 --> 00:14:35,050
Yo!

167
00:14:38,590 --> 00:14:41,923
I've come today to tell you
something important.

168
00:14:42,627 --> 00:14:45,755
From here on,
as my official disciple,

169
00:14:45,830 --> 00:14:48,822
I'll train you to become
a full fledged Shinobi in three years.

170
00:14:49,334 --> 00:14:50,596
Three years...?

171
00:14:51,269 --> 00:14:54,238
I've received some credible information
from a certain source

172
00:14:54,305 --> 00:14:55,567
concerning the Akatsuki.

173
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:57,239
<i>Akatsuki...</i>

174
00:14:58,643 --> 00:15:02,340
It seems that it will be
three or four years

175
00:15:02,414 --> 00:15:05,042
before they come after you next.

176
00:15:07,652 --> 00:15:09,347
I don't care about that!

177
00:15:10,455 --> 00:15:12,514
Talking about stuff that's
so far down the road...

178
00:15:12,590 --> 00:15:15,616
I don't have the time
to be doing slowpoke training!

179
00:15:16,294 --> 00:15:17,852
What do you mean?

180
00:15:18,563 --> 00:15:20,997
If I don't go after
Sasuke immediately,

181
00:15:21,066 --> 00:15:23,933
he might be killed by Orochimaru!

182
00:15:24,569 --> 00:15:29,472
<i>"Immortal" doesn't mean that</i>
<i>the flesh is being maintained as is.</i>

183
00:15:30,508 --> 00:15:32,442
<i>Before his body decays,</i>

184
00:15:32,510 --> 00:15:36,879
<i>a strong and new flesh will be made</i>
<i>into a vessel for his soul.</i>

185
00:15:41,052 --> 00:15:43,953
It seems you've learned
of the true purpose

186
00:15:44,022 --> 00:15:46,183
for Orochimaru seeking Sasuke...

187
00:15:46,324 --> 00:15:49,259
Huh?! Then that means you also knew?

188
00:15:49,994 --> 00:15:54,590
I was looking into
Orochimaru's Immortality Jutsu.

189
00:15:54,899 --> 00:15:56,457
It seems with that Jutsu,

190
00:15:56,534 --> 00:16:02,097
he can't reincarnate into
the next body for three years.

191
00:16:02,674 --> 00:16:07,771
And unable to wait for Sasuke,
he just recently reincarnated...

192
00:16:07,846 --> 00:16:12,545
It'll be okay for three years from now...
There is time.

193
00:16:13,151 --> 00:16:15,517
That's not a lie, is it?!

194
00:16:16,121 --> 00:16:17,713
Not a lie, is it?!

195
00:16:19,791 --> 00:16:20,951
Nope...

196
00:16:25,864 --> 00:16:27,456
However...

197
00:16:29,701 --> 00:16:32,465
Forget about Sasuke...

198
00:16:34,439 --> 00:16:38,739
Sasuke went to Orochimaru
on his own accord.

199
00:16:39,077 --> 00:16:41,910
No matter what you do,
he won't change.

200
00:16:44,783 --> 00:16:47,377
I've seen many Shinobi, so I know...

201
00:16:47,452 --> 00:16:50,785
Sasuke is the same kind
as Orochimaru.

202
00:16:53,158 --> 00:16:57,026
If you're thinking about bringing him back,
just forget it.

203
00:16:57,228 --> 00:17:00,425
That's something an arrogant fool
would do!

204
00:17:00,598 --> 00:17:06,298
He may be nothing to you
but he's my friend!

205
00:17:06,571 --> 00:17:09,039
Would a friend hurt his comrade?!

206
00:17:09,107 --> 00:17:12,338
Take a look at your current plight!

207
00:17:13,545 --> 00:17:14,637
This is...!

208
00:17:21,286 --> 00:17:24,221
Why? Why would you...?

209
00:17:24,789 --> 00:17:27,383
We were called Sannin together...

210
00:17:27,458 --> 00:17:30,484
Weren't we comrades
since we were kids?!

211
00:17:32,197 --> 00:17:35,564
In every regard,
you're a foolish guy, Jiraiya...

212
00:17:35,633 --> 00:17:38,761
You lack thought
in everything you do.

213
00:17:39,504 --> 00:17:43,907
That's why you didn't notice
what I was doing.

214
00:17:44,175 --> 00:17:48,271
Can't you rethink it, Orochimaru?

215
00:17:48,646 --> 00:17:50,045
Absurd!

216
00:17:51,049 --> 00:17:52,880
How can you be so stupid?!

217
00:17:55,186 --> 00:17:57,313
<i>No matter how much I wanted it...</i>

218
00:17:57,722 --> 00:18:00,691
<i>in the end, there was no way</i>
<i>he would come back.</i>

219
00:18:01,125 --> 00:18:05,994
<i>After the agony, all that's left was</i>
<i>my own powerlessness and regret.</i>

220
00:18:06,531 --> 00:18:11,093
<i>I don't want you to go through</i>
<i>the same thing...</i>

221
00:18:15,740 --> 00:18:18,709
If you're going to go after Sasuke,
then there'll be no training.

222
00:18:19,377 --> 00:18:21,402
I'll get Anbu Black Ops to watch you

223
00:18:21,479 --> 00:18:24,471
and depending on the case,
prohibit you from leaving the village.

224
00:18:26,684 --> 00:18:28,811
You're not just an ordinary kid...

225
00:18:29,354 --> 00:18:31,914
You possess the Nine Tail Fox.
That the Akatsuki is after!

226
00:18:32,357 --> 00:18:34,757
This is serious.
I'll just have to do that...

227
00:18:34,826 --> 00:18:38,523
if you're going to act on your own
without listening to what I say.

228
00:18:41,532 --> 00:18:43,830
Eventually, you're going to have to deal

229
00:18:43,843 --> 00:18:46,962
with guys more troublesome
than Orochimaru.

230
00:18:48,106 --> 00:18:50,301
Give up on Sasuke.

231
00:18:51,609 --> 00:18:54,237
Sooner or later this was
going to happen.

232
00:18:54,512 --> 00:18:58,039
Don't suffer anymore!
Forget and dismiss him.

233
00:18:58,883 --> 00:19:00,544
It's not just Jutsu or power...

234
00:19:00,685 --> 00:19:04,621
If you're a Shinobi, develop eyes that
can make the right judgment.

235
00:19:05,123 --> 00:19:08,024
And if you're going to live
as a Shinobi, become wise.

236
00:19:08,693 --> 00:19:10,422
If you remain a fool...

237
00:19:10,495 --> 00:19:12,986
the reality is that it will be tough
living in this world.

238
00:19:15,500 --> 00:19:16,592
Fine.

239
00:19:18,937 --> 00:19:21,770
If that's what being wise is...

240
00:19:21,839 --> 00:19:24,137
Then I'm fine being a fool for life!

241
00:19:25,977 --> 00:19:27,069
Even if by myself,

242
00:19:27,145 --> 00:19:31,172
I'll create even more awesome Jutsu
and save Sasuke no matter what!

243
00:19:31,249 --> 00:19:34,776
And, and,
I'll even kick the Akatsuki's butt!

244
00:19:50,234 --> 00:19:53,101
If someone like you
were to do it alone...

245
00:19:54,305 --> 00:19:55,932
the best you'd be able
to come up with

246
00:19:55,939 --> 00:19:58,976
would be some
stupid erotic Jutsu, anyway.

247
00:20:04,916 --> 00:20:06,508
It might somehow work out

248
00:20:06,584 --> 00:20:09,382
if you are a big fool and
not an ordinary fool...

249
00:20:09,687 --> 00:20:12,622
Be prepared once
you're out of the hospital,

250
00:20:12,690 --> 00:20:14,521
you big fool.

251
00:20:16,027 --> 00:20:17,654
See you then.

252
00:20:17,795 --> 00:20:19,092
Roger!

253
00:20:27,305 --> 00:20:30,706
- It's been seven years since...
...all the members gathered like this.

254
00:20:30,775 --> 00:20:33,676
Since Orochimaru left
the organization.

255
00:20:34,112 --> 00:20:37,673
That Orochimaru has gotten
the Sharingan.

256
00:20:37,749 --> 00:20:40,650
Itachi... Your little brother?

257
00:20:43,388 --> 00:20:45,253
Don't get hasty. Yeah.

258
00:20:45,356 --> 00:20:48,018
We'll kill Orochimaru eventually...

259
00:20:49,127 --> 00:20:51,493
More importantly,
there are only three years left.

260
00:20:51,896 --> 00:20:54,330
Can everyone accomplish
the work required of them?

261
00:20:54,532 --> 00:20:55,396
Huh?

262
00:20:55,900 --> 00:20:58,835
Yes, our goal is...

263
00:20:59,037 --> 00:21:04,339
to get everything,
including the Nine Tail Fox in question!

264
00:21:12,650 --> 00:21:17,314
<i>When I recalled the parts one by one,</i>

265
00:21:17,388 --> 00:21:23,691
<i>I felt as though</i>
<i>I had understood everything</i>

266
00:21:23,762 --> 00:21:34,263
<i>Faded words which I kept so close to me</i>

267
00:21:34,572 --> 00:21:44,038
<i>Speechless nights, a hint of warmth,</i>

268
00:21:45,784 --> 00:21:50,778
<i>and this distant yearning for you</i>

269
00:21:51,089 --> 00:22:00,088
<i>I live, simply repeating this cycle</i>

270
00:22:02,267 --> 00:22:11,801
<i>Held in my two hands</i>
<i>A droplet of time</i>

271
00:22:13,244 --> 00:22:22,243
<i>Softly clutching forgotten memories</i>
<i>Lost words</i>

272
00:22:31,129 --> 00:22:34,997
<i>I'll keep these thoughts...</i>

273
00:22:39,270 --> 00:22:43,172
Sakura's been weird all along
ever since Sasuke left.

274
00:22:43,508 --> 00:22:45,032
I can't put it well,

275
00:22:45,109 --> 00:22:47,907
but she's gloomy or fretting
or something.

276
00:22:48,413 --> 00:22:51,405
On top of that she says,
"This time I'll do my best on my own."

277
00:22:52,250 --> 00:22:54,650
What the heck does that mean?

278
00:22:54,886 --> 00:22:57,150
It's bugging me, it's bugging me!

279
00:22:57,222 --> 00:23:00,453
This isn't the time for me
to be relaxing in the hospital!

280
00:23:00,758 --> 00:23:05,457
Next episode:
"Deep Cover?! A Super S-Rank Mission"
